      desc 'Python extentions for text processing, date and crypto

egenix-mx-base provides extensions for Python that are a
collection of tools which enhance the usability of Python
in many important areas such as fast text processing,
ODBC database connectivity, date/time handling and
cryptographic applications.

The most popular of these extensions are mxDateTime providing
a library for doing date/time processing in Python and mxODBC,
the Python ODBC Interface for Windows and Unix.
Other important Python extensions included in the packages are
mxTextTools for lightning fast text parsing and mxBeeBase which
provides a cross-platform on-disk dictionary implementation.'
